Package: emojis
Type: Package
Title: Tools for analyzing text containing emojis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rebecca Godard
Maintainer: Rebecca Godard <rjgodard@mail.ubc.ca>
Description: Tools for counting emojis in texts, identifying the most common emojis in a text, and conducting sentiment analysis on text containing emojis using the NRC Emotion Lexicon and the NRC Emoji Lexicon.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    syuzhet,
    stringr
